==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Muscle reading
<hw>Mus"cle read`ing</hw>. <def>The art of making discriminations
between objects of choice, of discovering the whereabouts of hidden
objects, etc., by inference from the involuntary movements of one whose
hand the reader holds or with whom he is otherwise in muscular
contact.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Muscling</ent>⟦br⟧
